OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA rather cloudy start, with
OL,6,Foutbreaks of light rain and drizzle at
OL,7,Ftimes. Becoming mostly dry into the
OL,8,Fafternoon with some bright or sunny
OL,9,Fspells developing. Chance of a few
OL,10,Fshowers breaking out. Feeling warm in
OL,11,Fthe sunshine. Light winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FAny showers fading to give a
OL,14,Fdry night, with variable amounts of
OL,15,Fcloud and clear spells. Perhaps a few
OL,16,Fmist and fog patches forming by dawn.
OL,17,FLocally chilly. Light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
