OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FEarly mist and fog patches
OL,6,Fsoon clearing to give a largely dry
OL,7,Fday, with variable cloud and bright or
OL,8,Fsunny spells. Chance of a few light
OL,9,Fshowers in the afternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,12,FCloudy with patchy rain gradually
OL,13,Fclearing to leave mostly dry and
OL,14,Fbright conditions on Thursday.
OL,15,FBecoming unsettled with some rain at
OL,16,Ftimes Friday and Saturday. Often windy
OL,17,Fand relatively mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
